freedom of action the King Bishop has, since it travels on white squares only. } (8. e5 Ng4 9. Bf4 Bc5 { [%csl Rf2] } 10. Bg3 (10. f3 Nf2 11. Rg1 Nd3+ { [%csl Rg1] }) 10... Bd4 { [%csl Rb2,Re5] }) 8... e5! { A little move, but it accomplishes a great deal:
