control of the file, this is what might happen } 17. Ke3 (17. Nf1 Nb3 18. Rxd8 Rxd8 19. Rd1 Rxd1 20. Bxd1 Bxc4 { and White has lost a Pawn. }) 17... Rd7 18. g3 { The purpose of this move and White’s next, is to
