ending, Smyslov’s lone Bishop (one is all he needs, ap parently) travelling along the white squares, spreads terror among the enemy’s Pawns on the Queen side, fixed as they are on white squares. The whole game is in Smyslov’s best style, which is to say that it is a delight to play over. }
