entitled) from Foltys himself. The Knight clears the way, with gain of
tempo, for an advance of the c-Pawn which proves to have decisive effect. } { [%csl Rc7][%cal Gc2c4] } 16... Qf7 17. c4 { White’s moves are simple and strong. They are hard to meet, because they
