row. } { [%csl Yb5,Yc5,Yd5,Ye5,Yf5,Yg5][%cal Gd6c5] } 44. g4 fxg4 45. fxg4 Bc5 46. Be1 (46. Bxc5 Kxc5 { (I refrain from stressing the obvious.) }) 46... e4 47. dxe4+ Kxe4 48. Bd2 { Black can easily go wrong at this point. If he protects the threatened
