♗xg5 50 ♔b4 forces a draw. } 48... Be3 (48... Be7? 49. Bxg5 Bxg5 50. Kb4) 49. Be1 Kf3 50. Kb4 Kxg4 51. Kxb5 Kf3 { The last phase: getting the Pawn through without allowing White to
