dislodge the Bishop by c3, or open a file for his Queen Rook, affording him counter-play. } 13. a3! { A subtle trap! } (13. Bd2 Bxb2) 13... O-O (13... bxa3 14. Rxa3 { [%cal Gc2c3] } 14... Bxb2 15. Bxb2 Rxb2 16. Qa1 { (a strange attack on both Rooks!) } { [%csl Rb2,Rh8] } 16... Qb6 17. Nc4) 14. axb4 cxb4 15. Qe1 { Again with the idea of playing 16 c3 followed by 17
