lured into a deeply-hidden trap. In order to win the exchange, Fischer has had to weaken his Kingside ever so slightly, and this weakness is exploited by Olafsson through a series of clever moves. For a while it looks as though Fischer will equalize, but Olafsson plays it in fine style, and
